Enclosing class:
AlbumTemplatePrototype
public static class AlbumTemplatePrototype.Data<T extends >
extends

Instances of this class hold the prototype-data for creation of AlbumTemplate-s.
This class also functions as a base-class for AlbumTemplate-s and AlbumPrototype.Data.

getLargestImageSize

public Image.IMAGE_SIZE getLargestImageSize()
Images can be limited by size in which they are shown in this gallery/album on smugmug to prevent theft. The largest allowed size by this album is returned by this method.

Returns:
The largest allowed size.

setLargestImageSize

public void setLargestImageSize(Image.IMAGE_SIZE maxSize)
This is an alternative to calling one of the setIsLargest[xxxx]() methods. This specifies the largest image-size that can be shown by this album (or the album created from this album-template).

Parameters:
maxSize -
